  {
    "content_id": 797884,
    "reference_id": 17911,
    "title": "約珥書 2:11",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "29002011",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<ul><li><p>耶和華在隊伍的前面（字面意思是<em>耶和華在他的軍隊前發聲</em>；和合本譯為：耶和華在他軍旅前發聲）：即將到來的毀滅不僅只是自然現象或人類活動的結果，而是神的行動。</p></li><li><p>他的隊伍甚大：神執行了這個審判。</p></li><li><p>誰能當得起呢？若沒有神的恩典和憐憫，沒有人能當得起。</p></li></ul>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "29002011",
          "start_ref_usfm": "JOL 2:11",
          "end_ref": "29002011",
          "end_ref_usfm": "JOL 2:11"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 797886,
    "reference_id": 17913,
    "title": "約珥書 2:12",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "29002012",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<ul><li><p>這節經文以「耶和華說」起頭，這個片語常伴隨先知所說的神聖話語。這裡是約珥書中唯一一次出現這個用語（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Joel3:1\">3:1</a>中的「耶和華說」是由譯者所補充的），這表明這個恩慈的邀請是直接來自於神。</p></li><li><p>現在就轉向我，趁還有時間（和合本譯為：雖然如此，你們贏得……一心歸向我）：耶和華懇請祂的百姓悔改，因為審判的日子臨近了。如果他們真心地悔改歸向耶和華他們的神，就仍有機會逃避即將到來的毀滅。</p></li><li><p>與其他先知不同，約珥從未列舉猶大和耶路撒冷人所犯的罪行。也許這些罪行是如此明顯，以至於他覺得不需要羅列出來。</p></li></ul>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "29002012",
          "start_ref_usfm": "JOL 2:12",
          "end_ref": "29002012",
          "end_ref_usfm": "JOL 2:12"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 797885,
    "reference_id": 17912,
    "title": "約珥書 2:12–17",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "29002012-29002017",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>約珥呼籲百姓悔改，將自己交託給有憐憫之恩的神。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "29002012",
          "start_ref_usfm": "JOL 2:12",
          "end_ref": "29002017",
          "end_ref_usfm": "JOL 2:17"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 797887,
    "reference_id": 17914,
    "title": "約珥書 2:13",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "29002013",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<ul><li><p>在古代世界中，表達悲傷的一種方式就是撕裂自己的衣服（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen37:34\">創37:34</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam3:31\">撒下3:31</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs19:1\">王下19:1</a>）。</p></li><li><p>你們要撕裂心腸：在希伯來文中，心是思想、信念和意志的中心。神子民的悔改應該超越外在的表現，內心真正地悔改——改變他們的方向、優先次序和態度。<span>這只有在他們回轉歸向耶和華時才可能實現</span>。</p></li><li><p>因為他有恩典，有憐憫……有豐盛的慈愛：百姓唯一的盼望在於耶和華的慈愛本性（另見<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod34:6-Exod34:7\">出34:6–7</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num14:18\">民14:18</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh9:17\">尼9:17</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps86:15\">詩86:15，</a><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps103:8\">103:8，</a><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps145:8\">145:8</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jonah4:2\">拿4:2</a>）。神不想刑罰，而是想饒恕和恢復祂的子民。</p></li></ul>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "29002013",
          "start_ref_usfm": "JOL 2:13",
          "end_ref": "29002013",
          "end_ref_usfm": "JOL 2:13"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 797888,
    "reference_id": 17915,
    "title": "約珥書 2:14",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "29002014",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>誰知道呢？（和合本譯為：也未可知）約珥這個簡單的問題承認了神的絕對主權（另見<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jonah3:9\">拿3:9</a>）。神並不因為我們舉行了某些儀式就有義務要復興我們。饒恕僅從神聖的恩典而來，但約珥知道神樂意饒恕（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Joel2:13\">珥2:13</a>）。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "29002014",
          "start_ref_usfm": "JOL 2:14",
          "end_ref": "29002014",
          "end_ref_usfm": "JOL 2:14"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 797889,
    "reference_id": 17916,
    "title": "約珥書 2:15",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "29002015",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>約珥呼籲禁食和舉行嚴肅會來尋求神。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "29002015",
          "start_ref_usfm": "JOL 2:15",
          "end_ref": "29002015",
          "end_ref_usfm": "JOL 2:15"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 797890,
    "reference_id": 17917,
    "title": "約珥書 2:16",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "29002016",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>新郎……新婦：在古代以色列，新婚夫婦可豁免大多數的公民義務（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut24:5\">申24:5</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke14:20\">路14:20</a>），但在這種緊急情況下，所有人都要應召到聖殿向神呼求。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "29002016",
          "start_ref_usfm": "JOL 2:16",
          "end_ref": "29002016",
          "end_ref_usfm": "JOL 2:16"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 797891,
    "reference_id": 17918,
    "title": "約珥書 2:17",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "29002017",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>耶和華啊，求你顧惜你的百姓：在聖殿中，宗教領袖和所有百姓都在絕望的處境下做出唯一可能做的事：尋求神的憐憫和顧惜。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "29002017",
          "start_ref_usfm": "JOL 2:17",
          "end_ref": "29002017",
          "end_ref_usfm": "JOL 2:17"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 797894,
    "reference_id": 17921,
    "title": "約珥書 2:18",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "29002018",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>由於百姓和土地都遭受了神的審判，因此兩者都會成了祂發熱心要憐憫的對象。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "29002018",
          "start_ref_usfm": "JOL 2:18",
          "end_ref": "29002018",
          "end_ref_usfm": "JOL 2:18"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 797892,
    "reference_id": 17919,
    "title": "約珥書 2:18–27",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "29002018-29002027",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>神應許在不久的將來要復興祂子民的物質生活，使他們的田地、果園、葡萄園和羊群豐足。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "29002018",
          "start_ref_usfm": "JOL 2:18",
          "end_ref": "29002027",
          "end_ref_usfm": "JOL 2:27"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 797893,
    "reference_id": 17920,
    "title": "約珥書 2:18–3:21",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "29002018-29003021",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>到目前為止，約珥書聚焦在神對猶大和耶路撒冷的審判上，但從此處開始，它描述了神的恢復的應許。如果百姓真誠地悔改，神將以恩典回應他們。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "29002018",
          "start_ref_usfm": "JOL 2:18",
          "end_ref": "29002018",
          "end_ref_usfm": "JOL 2:18"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 797895,
    "reference_id": 17922,
    "title": "約珥書 2:19–20",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "29002019-29002020",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>五穀、新酒和油：神將恢復土地，使其再次結出果實。這將再次為獻祭和敬拜提供所需之物（見<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Joel1:10\">1:10</a>、<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Joel1:13\">13</a>）。神也會消滅北方入侵的軍隊。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "29002019",
          "start_ref_usfm": "JOL 2:19",
          "end_ref": "29002020",
          "end_ref_usfm": "JOL 2:20"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 797897,
    "reference_id": 17924,
    "title": "約珥書 2:21–22",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "29002021-29002022",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>不要懼怕：神的偉大拯救將是完全且徹底的。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "29002021",
          "start_ref_usfm": "JOL 2:21",
          "end_ref": "29002022",
          "end_ref_usfm": "JOL 2:22"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 797898,
    "reference_id": 17925,
    "title": "約珥書 2:23",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "29002023",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>秋雨、春雨：神將再次恢復正常的降雨模式，乾旱（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Joel1:12\">1:12</a>、<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Joel1:20\">20</a>）將得到扭轉。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "29002023",
          "start_ref_usfm": "JOL 2:23",
          "end_ref": "29002023",
          "end_ref_usfm": "JOL 2:23"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 797899,
    "reference_id": 17926,
    "title": "約珥書 2:25",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "29002025",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>耶和華應許會補<span>還</span>蝗蟲所造成的慘重損失（見<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Joel1:4\">1:4</a>、<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Joel1:10\">10</a>，及<span data-bnType=\"resourceReference\" data-resourceId=\"17904\" data-resourceType=\"TyndaleStudyNotes\">相應的研讀註釋</span>）。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "29002025",
          "start_ref_usfm": "JOL 2:25",
          "end_ref": "29002025",
          "end_ref_usfm": "JOL 2:25"
        }
      ],
      "resource": [
        {
          "reference_id": 17904,
          "content_id": 797877,
          "resource_code": "TyndaleStudyNotes",
          "label": "約珥書 1:4",
          "language": "zht"
        }
      ]
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 797900,
    "reference_id": 17927,
    "title": "約珥書 2:26–27",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "29002026-29002027",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>就讚美……耶和華——你們神的名：神應許恢復他們的農作物和食物供應，這應使猶大和耶路撒冷的百姓讚美和崇拜，承認耶和華在他們中間，並且唯有祂是神。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "29002026",
          "start_ref_usfm": "JOL 2:26",
          "end_ref": "29002027",
          "end_ref_usfm": "JOL 2:27"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 797901,
    "reference_id": 17928,
    "title": "約珥書 2:28–29",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "29002028-29002029",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>我要將我的靈澆灌凡有血氣的：在以色列，神的靈加給人能力的這恩賜，在以前只賜給特定的個人，如士師（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg3:10\">士3:10</a>，<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg15:14\">15:14</a>）、祭司（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr24:20\">代下24:20</a>）、君王（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam10:10\">撒上10:10</a>）和先知（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa61:1\">賽61:1</a>）。將來，聖靈將被賜給神所有的百姓，而無論其性別、年齡或社會地位。要實現摩西的願望——即每個以色列人都能成為先知（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num11:29\">民11:29</a>）——所有人都得要說預言和見異象。在<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts2:1-Acts2:47\">使徒行傳二章1至47節</a>中，彼得將這一應許擴展到聚集在耶路撒冷之已知世界的所有人，無論他們屬於哪個族群（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts2:39\">徒2:39</a>；另見<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal3:28\">加3:28</a>）。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "29002028",
          "start_ref_usfm": "JOL 2:28",
          "end_ref": "29002029",
          "end_ref_usfm": "JOL 2:29"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 797903,
    "reference_id": 17930,
    "title": "約珥書 2:28–32",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "29002028-29002032",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>先知超越了他的時代，看到了耶和華未來的日子，那時神要以從未見過的方式澆灌祂的靈，並向全人類彰顯神蹟奇事。使徒彼得引用了這段經文，認為在五旬節那天這些都得到了應驗（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts2:16-Acts2:21\">徒2:16–21</a>）。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "29002028",
          "start_ref_usfm": "JOL 2:28",
          "end_ref": "29002032",
          "end_ref_usfm": "JOL 2:32"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 797902,
    "reference_id": 17929,
    "title": "約珥書 2:28–3:21",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "29002028-29003021",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>在更遙遠的未來，神將恢複祂子民的屬靈生命，將祂的靈澆灌在所有以信心回應祂的人身上，並審判拒絕承認祂主權的人和國家。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "29002028",
          "start_ref_usfm": "JOL 2:28",
          "end_ref": "29003021",
          "end_ref_usfm": "JOL 3:21"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 797905,
    "reference_id": 17932,
    "title": "約珥書 2:30–31",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "29002030-29002031",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>未來神的靈的澆灌將伴隨著神蹟奇事。血、火和煙柱，以及日頭和月亮變暗，都是神降臨審判的徵兆（參<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Joel2:10\">2:10</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark13:24\">可13:24</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev6:12\">啟6:12</a>）。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "29002030",
          "start_ref_usfm": "JOL 2:30",
          "end_ref": "29002031",
          "end_ref_usfm": "JOL 2:31"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 797906,
    "reference_id": 17933,
    "title": "約珥書 2:32",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "29002032",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<ul><li><p>凡求告耶和華名的就必得救：求告耶和華的名不應該是絕望時的最後掙扎；它伴隨著終生的敬拜、服事以及與神相交（見<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen12:8\">創12:8</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps105:1\">詩105:1</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa12:4\">賽12:4</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom10:13\">羅10:13，</a><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom12:1-Rom12:2\">12:1–2</a>）。</p></li><li><p>耶和華所呼召的人是祂所揀選的餘民，是那些在審判中存活下來的敬拜祂的人（見<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs19:31\">王下19:31</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezra9:8-Ezra9:15\">拉9:8–15</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa10:20-Isa10:22\">賽10:20–22</a>）。</p></li></ul>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "29002032",
          "start_ref_usfm": "JOL 2:32",
          "end_ref": "29002032",
          "end_ref_usfm": "JOL 2:32"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 797911,
    "reference_id": 17938,
    "title": "約珥書 3:1–16",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "29003001-29003016",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>約珥在這裡預言了對列國的神聖審判，特別是對那些逼迫神子民的國家。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "29003001",
          "start_ref_usfm": "JOL 3:1",
          "end_ref": "29003016",
          "end_ref_usfm": "JOL 3:16"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 797920,
    "reference_id": 17947,
    "title": "約珥書 3:2–3",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "29003002-29003003",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<ul><li><p>耶和華將在約沙法谷聚集這世界的軍隊（字面意思是<em>萬民</em>）。這個山谷與猶大王約沙法無關（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs22:41\">王上22:41</a>）；這個名稱的意思是「耶和華審判的山谷」，這標示出這個地方將是神裁決各國命運之地（參<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Joel3:14\">珥3:14</a>）。</p></li><li><p>各國的罪行包括流放神的盟約百姓，以及在不人道的奴隸貿易中傷害無助的童子童女（參<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek27:13\">結27:13</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev18:13\">啟18:13</a>）。</p></li></ul>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "29003002",
          "start_ref_usfm": "JOL 3:2",
          "end_ref": "29003003",
          "end_ref_usfm": "JOL 3:3"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 797922,
    "reference_id": 17949,
    "title": "約珥書 3:4–6",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "29003004-29003006",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>腓尼基的泰爾城和西頓城以及非利士的城犯下了掠奪耶路撒冷珍寶，以及將城中的百姓作為奴隸賣給希臘人的罪行（見<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos1:6\">摩1:6</a>、<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos1:9\">9</a>）。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "29003004",
          "start_ref_usfm": "JOL 3:4",
          "end_ref": "29003006",
          "end_ref_usfm": "JOL 3:6"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 797923,
    "reference_id": 17950,
    "title": "約珥書 3:7–8",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "29003007-29003008",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>泰爾、西頓和非利士四境的人曾奴役以色列人，因此耶和華將懲罰他們，將他們的兒女賣為奴隸。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "29003007",
          "start_ref_usfm": "JOL 3:7",
          "end_ref": "29003008",
          "end_ref_usfm": "JOL 3:8"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 797924,
    "reference_id": 17951,
    "title": "約珥書 3:9",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "29003009",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>這節經文嘲諷地叫這些國家來向耶和華發動一場徒勞的戰爭，這最終將帶來他們的滅亡和審判。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "29003009",
          "start_ref_usfm": "JOL 3:9",
          "end_ref": "29003009",
          "end_ref_usfm": "JOL 3:9"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 797912,
    "reference_id": 17939,
    "title": "約珥書 3:10",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "29003010",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>要將犂頭打成刀劍：約珥有意地反轉了<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa2:4\">以賽亞書二章4節</a>和<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mic4:3\">彌迦書四章3節</a>的意象，命令各國動員一切資源迎接即將到來的戰鬥。即使是不適合爭戰的弱者<em>，</em>也必須參戰。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "29003010",
          "start_ref_usfm": "JOL 3:10",
          "end_ref": "29003010",
          "end_ref_usfm": "JOL 3:10"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 797913,
    "reference_id": 17940,
    "title": "約珥書 3:12",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "29003012",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>戰鬥將在約沙法谷進行（見<span data-bnType=\"resourceReference\" data-resourceId=\"17947\" data-resourceType=\"TyndaleStudyNotes\">3:2–3的研讀註釋</span>），在那裡耶和華將向他們所有人宣告審判。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "29003012",
          "start_ref_usfm": "JOL 3:12",
          "end_ref": "29003012",
          "end_ref_usfm": "JOL 3:12"
        }
      ],
      "resource": [
        {
          "reference_id": 17947,
          "content_id": 797920,
          "resource_code": "TyndaleStudyNotes",
          "label": "約珥書 3:2-3",
          "language": "zht"
        }
      ]
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 797914,
    "reference_id": 17941,
    "title": "約珥書 3:13",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "29003013",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>神將擊敗列國，像鐮刀收割穀物一樣，也像工人在酒榨中<span>踹</span>葡萄一樣（見<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa63:2-Isa63:3\">賽63:2–3</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev14:14-Rev14:20\">啟14:14–20</a>）。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "29003013",
          "start_ref_usfm": "JOL 3:13",
          "end_ref": "29003013",
          "end_ref_usfm": "JOL 3:13"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 797915,
    "reference_id": 17942,
    "title": "約珥書 3:14",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "29003014",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<ul><li><p>數以千計的人（字面意思是<em>咆哮，咆哮</em>；或<em>人群，人群</em>；和合本譯為：許多許多的人）：這個重複的希伯來文字詞捕捉到了巨大的人群所發出的混亂聲音。</p></li><li><p>斷定谷：谷的名字改變了（參<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Joel3:2-Joel3:3\">3:2–3</a>、<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Joel3:12\">12</a>），因為<span>此刻</span>耶和華的審判已經決定。</p></li></ul>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "29003014",
          "start_ref_usfm": "JOL 3:14",
          "end_ref": "29003014",
          "end_ref_usfm": "JOL 3:14"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 797916,
    "reference_id": 17943,
    "title": "約珥書 3:16",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "29003016",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>耶和華如獅子般從錫安咆哮，聲音震動天地，令罪人驚恐（見<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos1:2\">摩1:2</a>）。然而，這同一隻兇猛的獅子也是祂百姓的避難所。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "29003016",
          "start_ref_usfm": "JOL 3:16",
          "end_ref": "29003016",
          "end_ref_usfm": "JOL 3:16"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 797917,
    "reference_id": 17944,
    "title": "約珥書 3:17",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "29003017",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>你們就知道：神最終的目的是讓祂的子民認識祂並分享祂的聖潔屬性。他們必須明白唯有祂是神，祂從錫安——祂的聖山——治理所有的創造物（另見<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Joel2:27\">2:27</a>）。眼前唯一真正的安穩，以及未來唯一的盼望，都來自於神的同在。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "29003017",
          "start_ref_usfm": "JOL 3:17",
          "end_ref": "29003017",
          "end_ref_usfm": "JOL 3:17"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 797918,
    "reference_id": 17945,
    "title": "約珥書 3:18",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "29003018",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>祝福將從耶和華在錫安掌權的同在中流出（另見<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek47:1-Ezek47:12\">結47:1–12</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos9:13\">摩9:13</a>）。那裡將會有大量的甜酒和奶。聖殿——神在地上的居所——將成為永久滋潤乾旱之地的泉源（見<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech14:8\">亞14:8</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev22:1-Rev22:2\">啟22:1–2</a>）。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "29003018",
          "start_ref_usfm": "JOL 3:18",
          "end_ref": "29003018",
          "end_ref_usfm": "JOL 3:18"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 797919,
    "reference_id": 17946,
    "title": "約珥書 3:19",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "29003019",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>雖然猶大得到了恢復，但她的古老仇敵埃及和以東將因對神百姓犯下的罪行而遭受神的審判。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "29003019",
          "start_ref_usfm": "JOL 3:19",
          "end_ref": "29003019",
          "end_ref_usfm": "JOL 3:19"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 797921,
    "reference_id": 17948,
    "title": "約珥書 3:20–21",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "29003020-29003021",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>約珥預言的結尾與其開頭形成了對比。在<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Joel1:1-Joel1:20\">一章1至20節</a>中，猶大的未來似乎岌岌可危。蝗災和乾旱作為神聖審判的標誌，威脅著猶大的生存。現在約珥以神聖的應許作為結尾，猶大和耶路撒冷將存到萬代。每一代的神子民都將在神會掌管天地的盼望中得安息（另見<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa9:6-Isa9:7\">賽9:6–7</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan2:44\">但2:44</a>，<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan7:13-Dan7:14\">7:13–14</a>）。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "29003020",
          "start_ref_usfm": "JOL 3:20",
          "end_ref": "29003021",
          "end_ref_usfm": "JOL 3:21"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  }
]